83074e582cdba8bedff40fc653731ad18ca357bde8f1420e2e8a2a38998b951aebcb73ca5d51859be3b4d9bc1a0308836ca2bb612269edbc61b9dd6ebc7fdb2a  fix-null-pointer-dereference.patch"
